org.restsql.core

Class Factory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.restsql.core.AbstractFactory
      • org.restsql.core.Factory

  • public class Factory
extends AbstractFactory
    Creates implementations and also is a facade for other framework factories. Customize the framework with new factories that use custom API implementation classes. Use restsql properties to specify the implementation class names. Note: Factories are always singletons and always produce new objects on request.
    Author:
    Mark Sawers
